data.description: Fall in Love with this Impressive remodeled home.  Amazing screened pool, pool deck, bar area in the pool, jacuzzi, salt water system, French doors, the yard is fenced, adding that additional security to your loved ones. Sprinkler system, solar panels/battery for entire house, includes eco tankless hot water.  Roof replaced, AC replaced, kitchen remodel, and master bathroom remodeled. Separate formal living and dining rooms.  After a day of fun, you can relax in your family room next to your fire place.  Great Neighborhood and perfect location, with easy access to 417 and 408, UCF, Valencia College, Rollin College, Full Sail University, Lockheed Martin, Orlando International Airport, hospitals, downtown, and Waterford shopping area**HOA fees only $60.00 monthly. ** Walking distance to Publix Supermarket, Costco, Target, Lucky's Market, Ross, Starbucks, and restaurants.  **Important Note - House has a security system that includes audio and video surveillance. Minutes to Disney and Universal Studios Theme parks.  Excellent home for investment and/or corporate.  GREAT neighbors and lots of trees.  This includes an access key to the community tennis court and community pool.  Did you know that pictures for Miss Universe Puerto Rico 2019 were taken in this home pool area?
